complete their search and isolate the disruptive elements 
four of the universities are in the islands central and southern 
districts the stronghold of the peoples liberation front the 
other two are in the northeast 
the radicals launched a violent antigovernment campaign two 
years ago to protest peace overtures to tamil rebels fighting for an 
independent nation 
the government blames the radicals for more than 3500 political 
killings since then the extremists allege too many concessions were 
given to the minority tamils who make up 18 percent of the 
population 
