proposing cancellation of the program failed but the armed services 
panel did approve cutting 500 million from the programs 
procurement budget 
since then the pentagon announced late friday the first flight 
tests of the bomber 18 months behind schedule would be held 
during the next two weeks and on monday the bomber moved under its 
