bymaster product manager of sports and sporty cars for mazda motor 
of america sixtyfive percent of rx7 buyers are male and half are 
married he said sixtyseven percent have a college degree or more 
and the median household income is between 55000 and 60000 
though mazda now is promoting its newest twoseat car the 
miata which starts at 13800 the company said the rx7 will 
remain the miata is coming into the lower end of the sports car 
market because the rx7 has moved upscale a spokesman explained 
