director of engineering at denverbased telecommunications inc 
the nations largest cable television operator 
controlling interest in the company is held by greenberg and his 
brother richard greenberg frederick greenberg is chairman of first 
city national bank and trust co in new york 
the technology was purchased last year from from kent 
washbased northwest transforms inc which is now controlled by 
the greenbergs brooks said 
